ging all the settings manually.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The blocks were generated using WordPress 6.4.3 with a block theme with the most permissive theme.json settings possible. All presets are the defaults: Colors, duotones, font sizes, spacing sizes, shadows, width etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Each block has its own post, and is listed under its category: Design, Theme, Widget etc.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Inner blocks such as the column, button, and comment blocks do not have their own posts.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Blocks that support borders have a tag called \"Border\".</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Setting up</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Download the file, activate the WordPress importer plugin and import the file.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If you want to test the Author Biography block, you need to manually add a biography to the \"theme reviewer\" user.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If you want to test the template only blocks, such as archive title, you need to add these manually to a template.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips for testing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you use block themes with different settings and templates, or a classic theme, you may find that not everything works as you expected. This is not necessarily a bug with the block, the theme, or the test file. If you suspect that there are bugs, it will require further testing.<br /><br />For example:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If your theme does not have a spacing preset called \"7\", then spacing preset 7 will not work in your theme.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If your theme does not support drop cap you will not be able to turn drop cap off and on.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If the content block in your single template is not set to full width, then a full width block will not span the full width of the browser window.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What\'s not included</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Experimental blocks<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Forms</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Time to read</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Table of contents</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Every embed block</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Template only blocks<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Archive and search title</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Term description</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Comment count</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Comments link</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What it is not intended for</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Testing font families. No font families were included in this test, only default presets were used.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Testing blocks on WordPress versions below 6.4.3</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Accessibility testing</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Testing private or scheduled posts, long titles, posts with many categories, etc.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How you can help</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can help by reporting bugs, writing documentation, requesting features and submitting updates in the GitHub repository: <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/theme-test-data\">https://github.com/WordPress/theme-test-data</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','How to use the test data','','inherit','closed','closed','','353-revision-v1','','','2025-04-23 07:49:07','2025-04-23 07:49:07','',353,'https://192.168.1.10/?p=1727',0,'revision','',0),(1728,1,'2025-04-23 07:49:11','2025-04-23 07:49:11','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"https://192.168.1.10/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sample Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2025-04-23 07:49:11','2025-04-23 07:49:11','',2,'https://192.168.1.10/?p=1728',0,'revision','',0);
